{"tid":536546,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NASA成功研製火星用小型核反應爐　為火星基地提供能源","createTime":"2018-01-22T01:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T10:17:54.000Z","uid":53379,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"1caa685e002d5069a8209fb3fd87e17507fc8fc4","tid":536546,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T01:32:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>NASA成功研製火星用小型核反應爐　為火星基地提供能源</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國太空總署計劃未來在火星上進行一系列研究，而太空人到達火星，將面對能源問題。由於火星的太陽光較地球弱，太陽能發電未必滿足需求，而 NASA 最近就成功測試一款可在火星上使用的小型核反應爐裝置，可為早期登陸火星建立的基地提供能源。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/dims-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fdims-3.jpg&h=ea950041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國太空總署 (NASA) 聯同洛斯阿拉莫斯國家實驗室 (Los Alamos National Lavoratory) 成功開發一款小型核反應爐，名為「Kilopower」。此裝置可為火星探險提供足夠而穩定的電力。<br />\n<br />\n在火星上，太空人需要電解水來產生氧氣，日常生活用到的電子設備都需要用電，另外太空人還需要製造火箭用燃料讓他們能返回地球。這個小型核反應爐就可提供足夠能源。核反應爐的架構較簡單，也沒有蒸汽渦輪，可直接將反應產生的能量，透過熱導管帶到引擎轉換成動能，再於發電機中轉化為電能。在早期登陸火星時，毋須攜帶大量體積龐大且重量不輕的太陽能發電板。<br />\n<br />\n根據核反應爐本身的大小，發電量可在 1kW 至 10kW 之間，可供應不同電器使用。而且反應爐可串連在一起，只要大約 5 個就能供應一支小隊使用。<br />\n<br />\n目前「Kilopower」的小型實驗機已通過測試，一切運作正常。而開發者會留意其變化，直至本年 3 月，如一切正常的話，就會開始進行大尺寸實驗機的製作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bdMzFQOABcQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbdMzFQOABcQ&d=NfLHfgbwHVIQMAjoJl73sk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=75eabcf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bdMzFQOABcQ</a><br />\n資料來源: Engadget<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/01/20/marsnuclearreactor/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2Fmarsnuclearreactor%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=NfLHfgbwHVIQMAjoJl73sk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=9fae16dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/01/20/marsnuclearreactor/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"467a3544ae6c2d252ac2b30798f61f48e7b353a1","tid":536546,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T01:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8cded0ed6611165194049f883a0ef5610a4e0a8","tid":536546,"uid":57376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T01:45:05.000Z","msg":"火星基地其實係咪用黎俾有錢佬避難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89c740e2a2aa7afed6899baf82ea0f899e21c74","tid":536546,"uid":144064,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T01:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/fallout/images/2/2f/Fo4_fusion_core.png/revision/latest?cb=20160722002433\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Ffallout%2Fimages%2F2%2F2f%2FFo4_fusion_core.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20160722002433&h=5594f7ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b93954989a6447228f4bf45d32360e8c5bdfaf91","tid":536546,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T01:51:02.000Z","msg":"聽日唔洗返工？"},{"pid":"9070528b8a70570df5b69dd8c7d44bfff2579e87","tid":536546,"uid":103230,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T01:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://blog-001.west.edge.storage-yahoo.jp/res/blog-f6-42/black_knights_party/folder/899225/34/22221134/img_0?1206498648\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-001.west.edge.storage-yahoo.jp%2Fres%2Fblog-f6-42%2Fblack_knights_party%2Ffolder%2F899225%2F34%2F22221134%2Fimg_0%3F1206498648&h=06ad4482&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dde9a3f09211cf27ac2f862d24243e2c0bf6601a","tid":536546,"uid":28279,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T01:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Stirling engine"},{"pid":"8528923950f4e366f25d97f15e3bcf4257aaa9e9","tid":536546,"uid":57