s/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T02:44:20.000Z","msg":"你唔明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4285243d2cc39cff00774a0fa76e25436514a613","tid":536546,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c7d3d602e7a32a6cfecca7162c112cfa4776d8b","tid":536546,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6060a7f5985d6ad51bc8eb6dc64dc2a5c7b3a8b9","tid":536546,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"火星上面有沒有已知的鈾礦?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T02:35:51.000Z","msg":"火星探索仲留係執石仔既層面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T02:47:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/msl/news/msl20111020.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fmission_pages%2Fmsl%2Fnews%2Fmsl20111020.html&d=NfLHfgbwHVIQMAjoJl73sk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=2725766a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/msl/news/msl20111020.html</a><br />\n<br />\nMars Rover Carries Device for Underground Scouting<br />\n<br />\nAn instrument on NASA's Mars rover Curiosity can check for any water that might be bound into shallow underground minerals along the rover's path.<br />\n<br />\nThe Dynamic Albedo of Neutrons instrument, or DAN, will scout for underground clues to a depth of about 20 inches (50 centimeters). The Russian Federal Space Agency contributed it to NASA as part of a broad collaboration between the United States and Russia in the exploration of space. Sergey Saveliev, deputy head of the Russian Federal Space Agency, emphasized that the cooperation on this project serves as a continuation of the joint activities associated with the study of Mars to enhance the scientific return to the international community in the areas of Mars exploration and Mars knowledge. The accommodation and integ